    "k = 10 #number of variables for heatmap\n",
    "corrmat = train.corr()\n",
    "cols = corrmat.nlargest(k, 'SalePrice')['SalePrice'].index\n",
    "cm = np.corrcoef(train[cols].values.T)\n",
    "f, axes = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 5))\n",
    "cmap = sns.cubehelix_palette(light=1, as_cmap=True)\n",
    "hm = sns.heatmap(cm, cbar=True, annot=True, square=True, fmt='.2f', annot_kws={'size': 10}, \\\n",
    "                 yticklabels=cols.values, xticklabels=cols.values,cmap=cmap)"

    "numeric_feats = numeric_feats.drop(\"SalePrice\")\n",
    "def jointplot(x,y,**kwargs):\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        sns.regplot(x=x,y=y)\n",
    "    except Exception:\n",
    "        print(x.value_counts())\n",
    "f = pd.melt(train, id_vars=['SalePrice'],value_vars=numeric_feats)\n",
    "g = sns.FacetGrid(f,col='variable',col_wrap=3,sharex=False,sharey=False,size=5)\n",
    "g = g.map(jointplot,\"value\",\"SalePrice\")"

    "total = all_data.isnull().sum().sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
    "percent = (all_data.isnull().sum()/all_data.isnull().count()).sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
    "Type = all_data.dtypes\n",
    "missing_data = pd.concat([total, percent,Type], axis=1, keys=['Total', 'Percent','Type'])\n",
    "missing_data = missing_data[missing_data['Total']>0].sort_values(ascending=False,by = 'Percent')\n",
    "missing_data.drop(['SalePrice'])"
   ]

   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": true
   },
   "source": [
    "特征变量比较多,接近80个。可以把它们大致分为:\n",
    "*影响销售的一些总体因素,土地,设施及周边环境,房屋整体情况,房屋内部情况*\n",
    "这几个方面。在数据清洗及特征处理的过程中,边分析边处理。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 数据前处理<a id='数据前处理'></a>"
   ]

   "source": [
    "### 缺失值\n",
    "缺失值分为两种情况:\n",
    "    1.缺失值表示没有该特征;\n",
    "    2.缺失值确实是数据缺失。\n",
    "所以得视实际情况来分别处理。"
   ]

   ],
   "source": [
    "total = all_data.isnull().sum().sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
    "percent = (all_data.isnull().sum()/all_data.isnull().count()).sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
    "Type = all_data.dtypes\n",
    "missing_data = pd.concat([total, percent,Type], axis=1, keys=['Total', 'Percent','Type'])\n",
    "missing_data = missing_data[missing_data['Total']>0].sort_values(ascending=False,by = 'Percent')\n",
    "missing_data.drop(['SalePrice'])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 特征工程"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "一些离散变量,其含义是带有序列关系的,对于这类特征可以按需赋予连续值,这样也对后期的回归模型有利。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 31,
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": true
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "qual_dict = {'None': 0, 'Po': 1, 'Fa': 2, 'TA': 3, 'Gd': 4, 'Ex': 5}\n",
    "all_data['ExterQual'] = all_data['ExterQual'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['ExterCond'] = all_data['ExterCond'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['BsmtQual'] = all_data['BsmtQual'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['BsmtCond'] = all_data['BsmtCond'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['HeatingQC'] = all_data['HeatingQC'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['KitchenQual'] = all_data['KitchenQual'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['FireplaceQu'] = all_data['FireplaceQu'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['GarageQual'] = all_data['GarageQual'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "all_data['GarageCond'] = all_data['GarageCond'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data['BsmtExposure'] = all_data['BsmtExposure'].map(\n",
    "    {'None': 0, 'No': 1, 'Mn': 2, 'Av': 3, 'Gd': 4}).astype(int)\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data['Functional'] = all_data['Functional'].map(\n",
    "    {'None': 0, 'Sal': 1, 'Sev': 2, 'Maj2': 3, 'Maj1': 4, \n",
    "     'Mod': 5, 'Min2': 6, 'Min1': 7, 'Typ': 8}).astype(int)\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data['GarageFinish'] = all_data['GarageFinish'].map(\n",
    "    {'None': 0, 'Unf': 1, 'RFn': 2, 'Fin': 3}).astype(int)\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data['Fence'] = all_data['Fence'].map(\n",
    "    {'None': 0, 'MnWw': 1, 'GdWo': 2, 'MnPrv': 3, 'GdPrv': 4}).astype(int)\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data['PoolQC'] = all_data['PoolQC'].map(qual_dict).astype(int)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "针对地下室的情况,部分样本含有多种评价情况。因此考虑将其整合为一个变量，并为每种情况打分,最后合并为一个总分值。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 32,
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": true
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df1=all_data[['Id','BsmtFinType1','BsmtFinSF1']]\n",
    "df1.columns=['Id','BsmtFinType','BsmtFinSF']\n",
    "df2=all_data[['Id','BsmtFinType2','BsmtFinSF2']]\n",
    "df2.columns=['Id','BsmtFinType','BsmtFinSF']\n",
    "df=df1.append(df2, ignore_index=True)\n",
    "df=df.groupby(['Id','BsmtFinType'],as_index=False).sum()\n",
    "df=df.pivot(index='Id', columns='BsmtFinType', values='BsmtFinSF').drop(['None','Unf'],axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "df=pd.DataFrame(df.values,columns=['BsmtFinType_ALQ','BsmtFinType_BLQ','BsmtFinType_GLQ','BsmtFinType_LwQ','BsmtFinType_Rec'])\n",
    "\n",
    "df.fillna(0,inplace = True)\n",
    "\n",
    "df=pd.concat([df,all_data['TotalBsmtSF']],axis = 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "df['BsmtFinType_Unf']=df['TotalBsmtSF']-df['BsmtFinType_ALQ']-\\\n",
    "df['BsmtFinType_BLQ']-df['BsmtFinType_GLQ']-df['BsmtFinType_LwQ']-df['BsmtFinType_Rec']\n",
    "df['BsmtFinScore']=df['BsmtFinType_Unf']*1+df['BsmtFinType_LwQ']*2+df['BsmtFinType_Rec']*3+\\\n",
    "df['BsmtFinType_BLQ']*4+df['BsmtFinType_ALQ']*5+df['BsmtFinType_GLQ']*6\n",
    "\n",
    "#df['BsmtFinType_ALQ']=df['BsmtFinType_ALQ']/df['TotalBsmtSF']\n",
    "#df['BsmtFinType_BLQ']=df['BsmtFinType_BLQ']/df['TotalBsmtSF']\n",
    "#df['BsmtFinType_GLQ']=df['BsmtFinType_GLQ']/df['TotalBsmtSF']\n",

    "#df['BsmtFinType_Unf']=df['BsmtFinType_Unf']/df['TotalBsmtSF']\n",
    "#df.fillna(0,inplace = True)\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data.drop(['BsmtFinType1','BsmtFinSF1','BsmtFinType2','BsmtFinSF2','BsmtUnfSF'],axis=1,inplace = True)\n",

    "对右偏连续特征做对数处理"
   ]

   "cell_type": "code",

   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "numeric_feats = all_data.drop(['SalePrice'],axis = 1).dtypes[all_data.dtypes!=\"object\"].index\n",
    "\n",
    "from scipy import stats\n",
    "skewed_feats = all_data[numeric_feats].apply(lambda x: stats.skew(x.dropna())) #compute skewness\n",
    "cnt_feats=all_data[numeric_feats].apply(lambda x: len(pd.unique(x.dropna())))\n",
    "max_feats=all_data[numeric_feats].apply(lambda x:max(x.dropna()))\n",
    "df = pd.concat([skewed_feats,cnt_feats,max_feats],axis=1)\n",
    "df.columns = ['skew','cnt','max']\n",
    "#df.drop(['SalePrice'],inplace = True)\n",
    "skewed_feats = df.loc[(abs(df['skew'])>0.5)&(df['max']>1)&(df['cnt']>30)].index\n",
    "\n",
    "all_data[skewed_feats] = np.log1p(all_data[skewed_feats])\n",
    "all_data['SalePrice'] = np.log(all_data['SalePrice'])"
   ]
  },

    "## 4. baseline建模及评估<a id='baseline建模及评估'></a>"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 42,
   "metadata": {

   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "mean_rmse = {}\n",
    "mean_time = {}"

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 43,
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": true
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.model_selection import learning_curve\n",
    "def plot_learning_curve(estimator, title, X, y, ylim=None, cv=None,\n",
    "                        n_jobs=1, train_sizes=np.linspace(.1, 1.0, 5)):\n",
    "    plt.figure()\n",
    "    plt.title(title)\n",
    "    if ylim is not None:\n",
    "        plt.ylim(*ylim)\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Training examples\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Score\")\n",
    "    train_sizes, train_scores, test_scores = learning_curve(\n",
    "        estimator, X, y, cv=cv, n_jobs=n_jobs, train_sizes=train_sizes, scoring='neg_mean_squared_error')\n",
    "    train_scores = np.sqrt(abs(train_scores))\n",
    "    test_scores = np.sqrt(abs(test_scores))\n",
    "    train_scores_mean = np.mean(train_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    train_scores_std = np.std(train_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    test_scores_mean = np.mean(test_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    test_scores_std = np.std(test_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.grid(True)\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.fill_between(train_sizes, train_scores_mean - train_scores_std,\n",
    "                     train_scores_mean + train_scores_std, alpha=0.01,\n",
    "                     color=\"r\")\n",
    "    plt.fill_between(train_sizes, test_scores_mean - test_scores_std,\n",
    "                     test_scores_mean + test_scores_std, alpha=0.01, color=\"g\")\n",
    "    plt.plot(train_sizes, train_scores_mean, 'o-', color=\"r\",\n",
    "             label=\"Training score\")\n",
    "    plt.plot(train_sizes, test_scores_mean, 'o-', color=\"g\",\n",
    "             label=\"Cross-validation score\")\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.legend(loc=\"best\")\n",
    "    return plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 44,
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": true
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.model_selection import KFold\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error\n",
    "import time\n",
    "def kfold_plot(train, ytrain, model):\n",
    "    kf = KFold(n_splits=5)\n",
    "    rmse_scores = []\n",
    "    exe_time = []\n",
    " \n",
    "    i=0\n",
    "    for train_index, test_index in kf.split(train, ytrain):\n",
    "        X_train, X_test = train.iloc[train_index], train.iloc[test_index]\n",
    "        y_train, y_test = ytrain.iloc[train_index], ytrain.iloc[test_index]\n",
    "        begin_t = time.time()\n",
    "        model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "        predictions = model.predict(X_test)\n",
    "        end_t = time.time()\n",
    "        exe_time.append(round(end_t-begin_t, 3))      \n",
    "        \n",
    "        rmse_scores.append(np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test.astype(float), predictions))) \n",
    "        \n",
    "        i += 1\n",
    "\n",
    "    print ('mean rmse_scores: ', np.mean(rmse_scores))\n",
    "    print ('mean model process time: ', np.mean(exe_time), 's')\n",
    "    plot_learning_curve(model, \"Learning Curves\",train, ytrain,ylim=(0.01, 0.2),  n_jobs=1,cv=5)\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    return np.mean(rmse_scores),np.mean(exe_time)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "metadata": {

    "from mlxtend.regressor import StackingRegressor\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score\n",
    "\n",
    "srgs_model = StackingRegressor(regressors=[lasso_model, ridge_model,linearsvm_model, svm_model],\\\n",
    "                               meta_regressor=LinearRegression()\n",
    "                              )\n",
    "mean_rmse['stack'],mean_time['stack'] = kfold_plot(x_train[fs_l1], y_train, srgs_model)"
   ]

    "y = srgs_model.predict(x_test[fs_l1]) \n",
    "y=np.exp(y)\n",
    "obj = pd.Series(y,name = 'SalePrice')\n",
    "result = pd.concat([test['Id'],obj],axis=1)\n",
    "result.to_csv('result_stack.csv',index = False)"
